:PortaDOOM - <github.com/Kroc/PortaDOOM>
:===============================================================================
`PortaDOOM` is the work of _Kroc Camen_ and contributors and made possible only by the awesomeness of the `DOOM` community.

The WADs distributed with `PortaDOOM` may not match their original source downloads (i.e. checksum) due to extra compression applied by `DOOM-Crusher`, a tool for automatically optimizing WAD files and resources:
_<github.com/Kroc/DOOM-Crusher>_.

